<a href="../ko/programs/htdigest.html" hreflang="ko" rel="alternate" title="Korean">&nbsp;ko&nbsp;</a> |
<a href="../tr/programs/htdigest.html" title="T&uuml;rk&ccedil;e">&nbsp;tr&nbsp;</a></p>
